Detailed Description

cvmx_gmx::_rx_pass_en

GMX_RX_PASS_EN = Packet pass through mode enable

When both Octane ports are running in Spi4 mode, packets can be directly passed from one SPX interface to the other without being processed by the core or PP's. The register has one bit for each port to enable the pass through feature.

Notes: (1) Can only be used in dual Spi4 configs

(2) The mapped pass through output port cannot be the destination port for any Octane core traffic.
